      "cookedHtml": "<p>I’m trying to create a custom trigger but I can’t put it in the frame, I haven’t used this tool much could someone help me?</p>\n<p>trigger:<br />\n</p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/2X/7/7c95d20c010004daea6387cb2b21c882e024bb69.png\" title=\"image\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/optimized/2X/7/7c95d20c010004daea6387cb2b21c882e024bb69_2_550x500.png\" alt=\"image\" width=\"550\" height=\"500\" /><div class=\"meta\">\n<span class=\"filename\">image</span><span class=\"informations\">747×679 34 KB</span>\n</div></a></div><p></p>\n<p></p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/2X/8/8f2c833a9101ddf6075a8795428fa0ec3637b0bd.png\" title=\"image\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/optimized/2X/8/8f2c833a9101ddf6075a8795428fa0ec3637b0bd_2_598x500.png\" alt=\"image\" width=\"598\" height=\"500\" /><div class=\"meta\">\n<span class=\"filename\">image</span><span class=\"informations\">726×607 28.8 KB</span>\n</div></a></div><p></p>\n<p></p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/2X/d/dd4d91277d2be2540a0bc47257d992e144547d87.png\" title=\"image\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/optimized/2X/d/dd4d91277d2be2540a0bc47257d992e144547d87_2_409x374.png\" alt=\"image\" width=\"409\" height=\"374\" /><div class=\"meta\">\n<span class=\"filename\">image</span><span class=\"informations\">723×661 31.1 KB</span>\n</div></a></div><p></p>\n<p>action:</p>\n<p></p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/2X/9/983132937b80d82aa6b259e00f80952aacadebf5.png\" title=\"image\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/optimized/2X/9/983132937b80d82aa6b259e00f80952aacadebf5_2_555x500.png\" alt=\"image\" width=\"555\" height=\"500\" /><div class=\"meta\">\n<span class=\"filename\">image</span><span class=\"informations\">721×649 17.6 KB</span>\n</div></a></div><p></p>\n<p></p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/2X/7/7c5f88332983f8f09ef3b881f7cc1180afeb8984.png\" title=\"image\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/optimized/2X/7/7c5f88332983f8f09ef3b881f7cc1180afeb8984_2_546x499.png\" alt=\"image\" width=\"546\" height=\"499\" /><div class=\"meta\">\n<span class=\"filename\">image</span><span class=\"informations\">729×667 22.2 KB</span>\n</div></a></div><p></p>\n<p>When I try to add to the frame I can’t.</p>\n<p></p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/2X/4/40fe97b6e349dd8174d0c6190df9371bca03649e.png\" title=\"image\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/optimized/2X/4/40fe97b6e349dd8174d0c6190df9371bca03649e_2_690x325.png\" alt=\"image\" width=\"690\" height=\"325\" /><div class=\"meta\">\n<span class=\"filename\">image</span><span class=\"informations\">1815×855 46.3 KB</span>\n</div></a></div><p></p>"
