      "author": "basdebruin (Bas de Bruin)",
      "cookedHtml": "<p>hi <a class=\"mention\" href=\"/u/franklin.oliveira\">@franklin.oliveira</a></p>\n<p>Not sure if I can oversee everything form the screenshots. I am wondering why the boardId in the action part is set to “Context”, have you tried “Trigger output”?</p>\n<p>Also, what are the fields defined in the trigger output?</p>\n<p>This is a standard monday trigger, right? The post title confuses me a little <img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/slight_smile.png?v=10\" title=\":slight_smile:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":slight_smile:\" /></p>"
    },
