    {
      "id": 59873,
      "postNumber": 4,
      "createdAt": "2021-08-04T18:48:38.036Z",
      "author": "Helen (Helen)",
      "cookedHtml": "<p>Hi <a class=\"mention\" href=\"/u/franklin.oliveira\">@franklin.oliveira</a>!</p>\n<p>I agree with <a class=\"mention\" href=\"/u/basdebruin\">@basdebruin</a> here. I believe you’re running into this issue because you’ve defined the <code>boardId</code> field in your trigger as being “Recipe Sentence,” yet you’re not setting it anywhere. This is why the recipe can’t be added to your board-- because it’s not finished yet!</p>\n<p>Instead, if you switch it to “Context,” it should work.</p>"
    },
